There is a history of changing JSON message formats across past Exabgp versions, such that helper scripts need different message parse functions, depending on the version.
3.4.16 and 3.4.13 (and probably more) versions have 3.4.8 in the JSON messages, but this probably should be updated with each new version so that the version string in the JSON matches the actual Exabgp version that generates it.

